\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Having faced resistance from Evan, Patti chose to set aside her emotions and rally behind Evan\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s relationship with Sarah. Despite her belief that the relationship would ultimately lead to heartbreak, she resolved to support him. Patti conveyed her decision to the friends who had urged her to caution Evan against dating Sarah, encouraging them to follow her lead and back Evan\u8217\'92s choice. She emphasized the importance of standing by Evan, just as he would if the roles were reversed and he found himself in a similar situation.<!$Scr_Ps::3>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs18\b0\i0
\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf6 <$Scr_Ps::2>Leading Context:<!$Scr_Ps::2><$Scr_Ps::3>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 At the request of a few of Evan\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s close friends, excluding Guido, Patti had just confronted Evan, questioning his relationship with Sarah and expressing their concerns that she is not a good fit and that he may get his heart broken one day.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Initially, Evan snapped, and angry words were exchanged. But he quickly calmed down and asked Patti to support his relationship with Sarah. He had supported her in a past relationship where he disapproved of the boyfriend, but as a friend, he stuck by her and expected the same.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 At the end of the previous scene, Patti realized that friends support each other. She left Evan, letting him know she would talk to everybody and encourage them to support him as well.<!$Scr_Ps::3>}
