\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Time:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::1> About an hour after sunset<!$Scr_Cs::1>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Weather/Environment:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::1> Chilly and getting colder and windier. It was partly sunny during the day, and because the group was sweaty and working hard, they were not adequately dressed for the coldness of the after-sunset evening. On top of that, their sweat-soaked clothes were adding to the chill. Once Patti had updated them, they were more concerned about getting in a warm car than discussing Evan\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s situation.<!$Scr_Cs::1><!$Scr_Ps::4>}
