\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf6 <$Scr_Ps::2>Tone:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::1> The overall tone is one of acceptance of the situation. The friends are relieved that Patti addressed the situation with Evan. Although they remained concerned that Sarah will hurt Evan, they're ready to move on. When all is said and done, they had a great day working in the field as volunteers, and they are anxious to get home, share some ice-cold beers, and relax. It might be said that the pressure has been released. There's no need to discuss it anymore. Evan is with Sarah. It is what it is.<!$Scr_Cs::1><!$Scr_Ps::2><$Scr_Ps::3>}
